abstract: New Jersey State Police find fishing trawler El Jefe, which sank in Sandy Hook Channel, but are unable to locate boat's captain Tom Andresen, who is believed to have been aboard.
lead_paragraph: Investigators used sonar to locate to boat, which was seen taking on water Tuesday afternoon about two miles offshore in the Sandy Hook Channel.

headline.main: New Jersey Police Find Sunken Fishing Boat, but Captain Remains Missing
headline.print_headline: Sunken Boat Found Off New Jersey; Captain Is Still Missing
